eNCA reporter Nqobile Madlala reports. #dstv403 DURBAN - Rapper AKA has left a big hole in the hearts of many who loved his music and those who shared the industry with him. The award-winning rapper and his former manager and friend Tebello Motsoane, TIBZ,  were shot and killed on Florida road in Durban on Friday night. Artists gathered in the same area today to pray, and celebrate the lives of the two. eNCA reporter Nqobile Madlala reports. #eNCA's Nqobile Madlala has the details. #DStv403